rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0003
rows.name:
I wonder why that Minochi
guy joined our group.

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0004
rows.name:
Beats me.
I guess grown-ups have their reasons.

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's try to ask next time
we take a break, if we get a chance.

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0007
rows.name:
But aren't we supposed to
be hurrying to the capital?

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0009
rows.name:
W-well... grown-ups have
their reasons for that, too.
